longBusinessSummary: Qliro AB (publ) operates as a fintech company. It provides digital checkout payment solutions to both enterprise and small and medium enterprise merchants in the Nordic region, as well as offers online pay-after-delivery products, including invoicing, Buy Now Pay Later, and various partial payments. The company offers personal loans and savings accounts, as well as consumer and digital financial services to consumers in Sweden. Its payment solutions include payment methods offered through card, direct payments from bank accounts and other payments. The company was incorporated in 2014 and is headquartered in Stockholm, Sweden. Qliro AB (publ) is a subsidiary of Nelly Group AB (publ).
